      "details": "\n            \n        <div class=\"card-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"row hpt-3 hmr-6\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 mt-2\">\n                    <h2 class=\"jobtitle mb-1 pb-1\">Marketing Assistant</h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <h2 class=\"opportunity-company mb-1 pb-1\">TK Marketing</h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                <div class=\"row verified mb-3 mt-0\">\n                    <div class=\"col\">\n                        <p class=\"verified-text\"><i class=\"icon icon-check2-circle\" style=\"margin-right:2px;\"></i><span>Partner Opportunity</span></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <div class=\"card-detail-meta mt-0\">\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-geo-pin-solid\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Location: </strong>Rustenburg, North West</p>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-calendar-event-solid\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Date posted:</strong> 15 May 2024</p>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-calendar-x\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Closing date:</strong> 14 June 2024 </p>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-briefcase\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Job type: </strong>Full-time / permanent</p>\n                            </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <h6 class=\"opportunity-reference mb-3 mt-3\">Reference number: 1454576</h6>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col text-break\">\n                            <h2>Role description</h2>\n                            <p class=\"text-break white-space-pre-line\"></p><p>Are you looking for an entry-level position that offers the opportunity to make a big difference in a firm? TK Marketing, a marketing and sales firm based in Benoni, has an exciting new opening for you.</p>\n<p>As an Entry Level Marketing Associate, you will contribute to one of our most important company initiatives: client representation and branding.</p>\n<p>Our company is seeking an adaptable, positive, and passionate team player who is willing to learn all facets of our company in order to ensure the success of our projects within our overall mission. You should be comfortable interacting with potential clients and customers, be solution-oriented, and have the ability to work with a wide variety of individuals. As this is an entry-level position, no direct experience is required. However, familiarity with marketing and sales basics, having a customer-focused attitude, and a desire for leadership will formulate the foundation of a great candidate. This position reports to the Market Manager and is a valued member of the overall marketing team.</p>\n<p>Responsibilities of the Entry Level Marketing Associate:</p>\n<p>* Become well versed in client product knowledge and services provided while maintaining a good working knowledge of the competition.<br>* Create and conduct sales presentations to customers and clients during in-field residential marketing campaigns.<br>* Communicate daily with team members on progress in the campaign and game plan for solutions and continued success.</p>\n<p><br><br></p><p></p>\n                            <h2>Role requirement</h2>\n                            <p class=\"text-break white-space-pre-line\"></p><p>Requirements of the Entry Level Marketing Associate:</p>\n<p>* Matric certificate or equivalent qualification* Must be between the ages of 18-28</p>\n<p>* An interest in direct marketing, field marketing and sales, field sales, brand management, or a customer-focused position as an asset.</p>\n<p>* Comfortable with public speaking and presentation or the desire to enhance these skills with training</p>\n<p>* Quick learner and adaptable</p>\n<p>* Organized, well-spoken and ready to be challenged</p>\n<p>* Experience in leadership is a plus</p><p></p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n\n                                <hr>\n                                \n        </div>\n    ",
